Ruth Matteson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ruth_Matteson 0 Ruth Matteson (December 10, 1910 – February 5, 1975) was an American actress. She appeared in more than 20 Broadway plays and had a variety of television roles. Ruth_Matteson ( December_10_,_1910 – February_5_,_1975 ) was an_American_actress .
